      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4980-5025",
      "markText": "我模糊地意识到安德蕾是因这种白色窒息而亡。坐火车之前，我在那些洁白的鲜花上放了三朵红玫瑰。",
      "totalCount": 1770,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43168695&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4980&rangeEnd=5025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7d3323a07292b3b77d31cf8?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4980&rangeEnd=5025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43168695_8_10175-10274",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10175-10274",
      "markText": "我第一次清醒地意识到，在这微笑背后隐藏着一个陷阱。从前我经常羡慕安德蕾享有的独立，突然之间，我觉得她没有我自由。在她身后有这段历史，在她周围有这座大宅、有这样一个大家族：一间牢狱，出路有人仔细把守。",
      "totalCount": 1650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43168695&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10175&rangeEnd=10274",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7d3323a07292b3b77d31cf8?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10175&rangeEnd=10274"
    },
    {
